default1.3default&#xa0; 
defaultMost bus routes are on local highway authorities’ winter salting/gritting or snow clearance rout
defaulte
defaults, and therefore are kept clear for bus services to continue to operate in all but the most extreme conditions.  However some services on more min
defaultor roads may be affected by adverse weather conditions, where the local authority has not cleared the route, with bus operators unable to provide services on those routes
default.
